317
00:19:32,660 --> 00:19:34,080
Could it be...

318
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:35,420
Yes?

319
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:38,410
Would she want you in the video with her?

320
00:19:38,410 --> 00:19:39,600
Hey!

321
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:41,330
