324
00:19:45,080 --> 00:19:46,230
"Get things in order"?

325
00:19:46,230 --> 00:19:50,710
Could she be getting rid of me?

326
00:19:50,710 --> 00:19:54,010
Did you do something she's not happy with?

327
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:55,530
I don't know.

328
00:19:55,530 --> 00:19:58,280
She nitpicks at everything I do, even the tiniest things.

329
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:01,790
You probably did something but didn't take a hint.

330
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:04,360
Maybe.

331
00:20:06,090 --> 00:20:09,390
Liking someone and all that

332
00:20:09,390 --> 00:20:11,510
isn't easy.

333
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:13,810
You should do better.

334
00:20:13,810 --> 00:20:15,100
All right?

335
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:17,450
Ho Sung.

336
00:20:19,030 --> 00:20:21,300
What's this strange atmosphere?

337
00:20:21,300 --> 00:20:25,240
   

338
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:29,230
 But it's obvious. 

339
00:20:29,230 --> 00:20:34,160
 The person that Kang Seo Young would go out of her way to protect. 

340
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:37,090
 Jung Young Joo. A new kid in my class. 

341
00:20:37,090 --> 00:20:39,730
 I heard Kang Seo Young dumped Jung Young Joo. 

342
