359
00:22:02,970 --> 00:22:06,200
housing in a dormitory for four years,

360
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,930
and a full scholarship.

361
00:22:08,930 --> 00:22:10,670
How do those sound?

362
00:22:12,380 --> 00:22:15,810
Why me, all of a sudden?

363
00:22:17,950 --> 00:22:23,220
I heard... you saw Young Joo throw the flowerpot.

364
00:22:28,890 --> 00:22:34,150
