367
00:22:43,090 --> 00:22:44,810
We have evidence,

368
00:22:44,810 --> 00:22:48,850
and I'm sure we can find a witness somewhere.

369
00:22:48,850 --> 00:22:53,260
In other words, nothing changes even if you don't testify.

370
00:22:53,260 --> 00:22:58,790
I simply want to give you an opportunity.

371
00:23:01,600 --> 00:23:04,700
You're more tender-hearted than I thought, Seo Young.

372
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:09,510
There's no need to feel bad for a friend.

373
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:11,580
You're doing the right thing

374
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:17,690
and admission to Jin Sung University is like a reward for your hard work all these years.

375
00:23:19,810 --> 00:23:22,000
Think about it.

376
00:23:23,570 --> 00:23:27,910
There isn't much time, so don't think about it for too long.

