00:23:58,110 --> 00:23:59,470
   

378
00:24:05,770 --> 00:24:07,620
Kang Seo Young.

379
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:14,420
Is something going on?

380
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:19,160
I saw you leaving Director Gu's office.

381
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,480
What is it?

382
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:22,500
What did Director Gu say?

383
00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:26,610
It's nothing.

384
00:24:27,430 --> 00:24:31,170
You look pale. Are you sure it's nothing?

385
00:24:35,810 --> 00:24:38,150
I think I told you already.

386
00:24:39,040 --> 00:24:42,160
You don't have to care about me anymore. Our deal is off.

387
00:24:42,890 --> 00:24:46,630
Or did you always mind other people's business?

388
00:24:46,630 --> 00:24:49,010
Why do you say it like that?

389
00:24:49,010 --> 00:24:50,840
Can’t we be friends without the deal?

390
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:53,740
I never said I wanted to be friends with you.

391
00:25:06,530 --> 00:25:10,790
Using Kang Seo Young to expel Jung Young Joo...

392
00:25:10,790 --> 00:25:12,800
That's a great plan.

393
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:17,500
Why would I inconvenience Jin Sung University's president

394
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:21,290
just to expel Jung Young Joo?

395
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:26,210
That's not what's important.

396
00:25:26,840 --> 00:25:28,200
Then...

397
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:31,160
If our victory is definite,

398
00:25:32,850 --> 00:25:36,800
I think we have a chance of overturning the trial.

399
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:39,940
Jung Cheol Joo's trial, that is.

400
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,130
Have a good night.

401
00:25:59,130 --> 00:26:01,220
Good work today. Bye.

402
00:26:12,930 --> 00:26:14,370
Did you get off work just now?

403
00:26:14,370 --> 00:26:15,470
Pardon?

404
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:17,100
Oh... yes...

405
00:26:17,100 --> 00:26:20,630
Ah... Are you restocking dolls today?

406
00:26:20,630 --> 00:26:22,030
Yes.

407
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:35,410
Don't come.

408
00:26:54,850 --> 00:26:57,070
 Don't come. Don't come yet! 

409
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,770
I saw someone else restocking them last time.

410
00:27:01,770 --> 00:27:04,430
I wondered if you weren't doing it anymore.

411
00:27:04,430 --> 00:27:10,700
Our assigned areas change periodically.

412
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:14,240
Oh... I see.

413
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:18,610
This is my last stop today.

414
00:27:18,610 --> 00:27:21,600
If you're free, do you want to grab something to eat?

415
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:24,220
Pardon? Oh... Oh...

416
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:27,870
Mom called earlier and said  to get home quickly.

417
00:27:27,870 --> 00:27:29,290
Too bad.

418
00:27:29,290 --> 00:27:32,360
Then should I take you home?

419
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:35,270
What? Oh... no, it's okay.

420
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:37,190
I'll get home quickly.

421
00:27:38,470 --> 00:27:39,980
Okay then.

422
00:27:39,980 --> 00:27:41,740
Get home safe.

423
00:27:41,740 --> 00:27:43,320
See you tomorrow.

424
00:28:24,360 --> 00:28:27,550
 How am I supposed to tell Young Joo? 

425
00:28:27,550 --> 00:28:30,710
 What if Young Joo hates Ki Joon again because of me, 

426
00:28:30,710 --> 00:28:33,210
 and they grow further apart? 

427
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:36,200
 No way... 

428
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,250
 No. 

429
00:28:37,250 --> 00:28:38,450
 Still... 

430
00:28:38,450 --> 00:28:39,810
Hey.

431
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:42,250
What are you thinking about?

432
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:45,230
It's nothing.

433
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:50,880
It's cold.

434
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,510
Let's hurry and go home.

435
00:28:57,720 --> 00:29:01,150
Wow, so pretty.

436
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:13,460
We almost got caught.

437
00:29:18,390 --> 00:29:20,280
We don't know them anyway.

438
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,920
Still.

439
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:31,650
So... Why do we have to keep it a secret?

440
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:35,230
It's not like we're doing anything wrong.

441
00:29:37,230 --> 00:29:38,880
I don't know.

442
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:42,820
It just feels like we have to.

443
00:29:45,490 --> 00:29:47,400
I think I know.

444
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,770
What?

445
00:29:50,030 --> 00:29:51,830
Just wait.

446
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:53,700
I'll take care of it.

447
00:30:07,170 --> 00:30:08,890
Ki Joon.

448
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,280
What's up this late at night?

449
00:30:21,050 --> 00:30:23,390
I have something to say to you.

450
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:27,140
You can tell me tomorrow at school.

451
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:29,320
