452
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:33,420
It will only get harder if I put it off.

453
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:40,600
Ji Won and I aren't just friends anymore.

454
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,960
We're dating now.

455
00:30:50,850 --> 00:30:52,830
It's not that surprising.

456
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:54,340
Isn't it?

457
00:30:55,450 --> 00:30:58,060
I can't really congratulate you, though.

458
00:30:59,620 --> 00:31:02,610
Did you run here in the middle of the night to say that?

459
00:31:03,300 --> 00:31:05,100
That is...

460
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:08,100
I thought you should be the first to know.

461
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:09,860
Don't be so dramatic.

462
00:31:12,870 --> 00:31:16,040
I'll be good to her.

463
00:31:16,930 --> 00:31:18,180
Whatever.

464
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:19,950
Now get lost.

465
00:31:21,010 --> 00:31:22,440
Hey—

466
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:33,130
Yes.

467
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:39,380
Here. The book you wanted to read.

468
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:41,120
Okay.

469
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:43,370
What are you doing still awake?

470
00:31:44,570 --> 00:31:46,210
Nothing much.

471
00:31:48,050 --> 00:31:50,390
Why was Ki Joon here earlier?

472
00:31:50,390 --> 00:31:52,730
