491
00:33:47,850 --> 00:33:49,730
Hey. Don't you dare.

492
00:33:49,730 --> 00:33:51,400
Please. Ki Joon.

493
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:55,120
Oh. I didn't subscribe.

494
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,560
What?

495
00:33:57,930 --> 00:34:00,160
- I'll do it. 
 - Don't do it, Gong Ki Joon!

496
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,560
Don't do it. You're my friend.

497
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:03,160
Is it me or Go Eun Bi? Don't do it.

498
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:05,450
Hey, Jin Ji Won.

499
00:34:05,450 --> 00:34:08,780
We got you, Jin Ji Won.

500
00:34:09,890 --> 00:34:12,780
What did I do? Who said so?

501
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:14,600
The president of the Machinery Department's Class Two.

502
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:17,720
She saw you walking home holding someone's hand.

503
00:34:17,720 --> 00:34:20,710
He was wearing our school uniform.

504
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:22,870
How would she know me?

505
00:34:22,870 --> 00:34:25,880
Think of all the days you protested at the school gate.

506
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:28,650
It would be weird if people didn't know your face.

507
00:34:29,850 --> 00:34:33,590
Am I that famous? I didn't know.

508
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:36,580
Who is it, seriously? I'm disappointed, Jin Ji Won.

509
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:39,270
