510
00:34:39,270 --> 00:34:40,840
It's nothing.

511
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,060
I don't think so.

512
00:34:42,060 --> 00:34:44,970
You ditched us when we went to eat your favorite jjolmyeon.

513
00:34:44,970 --> 00:34:46,390
You're suspicious.

514
00:34:46,390 --> 00:34:48,800
Who is it? Spill it, now.

515
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,000
- Speak up. 
 - Hurry.

516
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:52,790
- If you don't, you're betraying us. 
 - There are no secrets between us.

517
00:34:52,790 --> 00:34:55,520
- Hurry. Tell us. 
 - So disappointing.

518
00:34:55,520 --> 00:34:57,390
That's enough.

519
00:35:06,010 --> 00:35:07,700
Gong Ki Joon, what are you doing?

520
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:10,070
