 - You fooled us.

537
00:35:52,690 --> 00:35:54,120
Really?

538
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:57,090
- Are you guys dating? 
 - Since when?

539
00:35:57,090 --> 00:35:59,390
Is it true?

540
00:35:59,390 --> 00:36:01,080
Hey. Did you know about this?

541
00:36:01,080 --> 00:36:02,150
No.

542
00:36:02,150 --> 00:36:03,370
Hey, Gong Ki Joon.

543
00:36:03,370 --> 00:36:05,270
Hey, Gong Ki Joon. Jin Ji Won, tell me.

544
00:36:05,270 --> 00:36:06,930
No, Gong Ki Joon, you tell me.

545
00:36:06,930 --> 00:36:08,210
You said you were best friends.

546
00:36:08,210 --> 00:36:10,200
