547
00:36:10,200 --> 00:36:12,630
- My God! 
 - Really?

548
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:14,970
Ki Joon's a man.

549
00:36:14,970 --> 00:36:18,250
- Oh, my God!

550
00:36:19,530 --> 00:36:21,390
Young Joo—

551
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:28,280
So...

552
00:36:29,930 --> 00:36:31,590
Congratulations.

553
00:36:36,010 --> 00:36:37,830
